    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged but does not preclude acceptance given the strong performance across all other factors and the direct applicability of ASTM F1717 as the regulatory standard for this device class. The literature-based benchmarking activity provided supporting evidence consistent with published biomechanical data for comparable pedicle screw constructs.",
